    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are no chips, scratches, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in like-new condition, with the leather upholstery and trim showing virtually no signs of wear. Every mechanical and electronic feature functions perfectly, as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been maintained to the highest possible standard.",
