    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is ready for someone with a vision to take the reins. While it's currently in poor condition and will need some significant mechanical attention and a bit of TLC to get back to its prime, it represents a fantastic, budget-friendly opportunity for a restoration project or a reliable source of parts. If you love working with your hands and bringing a car back to life, this is the perfect canvas for you!",
      "price": 4500.0,
